Author: milkeyedmenders
Text: i think my thought process is like: hell ya i did it! so i have “permission” to celebrate and eat a million calories, even tho that will in fact add up and make me not this weight anymore and i’ll hate myself for it. but fuck the consequences i’m so god damn hungry

Author: thefakemexoxo
Text: There’s something stupid our mind does with check points. It’s like it passes a milestone and loses all focus.
